data.description:
SELLER IS MOTIVATED - SEND US YOUR OFFER.  HOA requires the Buyer to pay a 6 month reserve at the closing table.  GOOD NEWS FOR THE BUYER(S)! The Seller will credit the Buyer(s) the 6-month reserve amount at closing (i.e., $593.00 x 6 Mo. = $3,558.00).  This credit amount is not to exceed $3,558.00.  This fee does not apply to Buyer(s) regular monthly dues. When the property is resold, the reserve shall be given back to the Buyer(s) by the HOA at future closing.  MORE GOOD NEWS FOR THE BUYER(S)!  SELLER WILL ALSO CREDIT $2,000 TO THE BUYER FOR ANY UPGRADES (i.e. Paint, Carpet, etc. or to assist with closing costs).  

Enjoy the Heather Gardens lifestyle in this 55+ active resort-style community.  Situated on the first floor (no stairs or elevators).  This unit has it's own laundry room (washer/dryer included).  Brand new luxury wood laminate flooring throughout. The generous primary bedroom has an updated bathroom with a walk-in shower.  It also offers a palatial walk-in closet. The secondary bedroom is directly across the hall to an updated full bathroom.  Underground parking spot #37 with "cowboy storage" and there is more secured assigned storage located on the second floor. This community offers residents over 100 leisure activities, clubs and classes.  The 55,000 sq. ft. clubhouse features front desk, on-site HOA, 24- hour security, a golf course, a a golf shop, swimming pools, tennis courts, fine dining at the Rendezvous Restaurant which is open to the public, and an exercise facility are all definite must-sees. There is an indoor pool with lap lanes and an exercise facility with a sauna and lockers, a 2,320 sq. ft. multi-use auditorium for aerobics and other exercise classes, activity spaces and they even have space to rent out for your special events.  This is a smoke-free 55+ active community!  This unit is priced to sell.
